pageContext.claim: “Joe Biden has no clue. He's being pulled to the left to a level that nobody ever thought possible -- far further left than Bernie Sanders ever dreamt.”
pageContext.analysis: In fact, Biden is a moderate Democrat who has been endorsed by a host of mainstream Republicans, who prevailed in the Democratic primary by running to the right of the self-styled "democratic socialist" candidate, Bernie Sanders, and whose positions are seen as liberal but middle of the road for the Democratic Party.
